data.description: Welcome to Windsor Estates in McDonough, Georgia! Nestled in a peaceful neighborhood, this exquisite 4-sided brick estate offers the epitome of comfort and style. Boasting 7 bedrooms and 5 bathrooms, this home provides ample space for a growing family or those who love to entertain.  As you enter through the door, you'll be greeted by an impressive foyer that sets the tone for the entire residence. The main level features an open floor plan seamlessly connecting the spacious living area, gourmet kitchen, and dining room. Hardwood floors, high ceilings, and large windows contribute to an airy and inviting atmosphere. The gourmet kitchen is equipped with top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and a center island. There is a large bedroom with a walk-in closet and full bath on the main floor, perfect for a Mother-in-Law suite. The laundry room is on the main floor as well. The owner's suite is a true retreat. With an expansive sitting room, his and hers walk-in closets, double vanity, separate shower and soaking tub. This room will not disappoint. There are 3 additional bedrooms on the second floor. One with a private bathroom, vaulted ceilings, and a picturesque view of the lake. The other 2 bedrooms share a bathroom, each with their own sink. Each bedroom offers ample closet space and large windows, allowing natural light to fill the rooms. The third floor includes a bedroom with an attached bathroom, another bedroom perfect for a home office, and a loft area for a crafting or an entertainment area. Step outside to a well-manicured lawn enclosed with a 6' privacy fence. The property also includes a 12x16 storage shed. Conveniently located in McDonough, you'll have easy access to local amenities, schools, and shopping, making this property not just a home but a lifestyle. Don't miss the opportunity to make this magnificent 7-bedroom, 5-bathroom brick estate yours. Seller will provide the buyer $5,000 in seller credit for the carpet. Schedule a showing today.
